{
  "texts": [
    "Another challenge lies in efficiently storing large point clouds in a permutation-invariant file format.",
    "LiDAR technology, in particular, can generate massive file sizes, posing storage and processing problems.",
    "Furthermore, the data quality directly depends on the quality of the sensors used; higher quality data often requires more expensive sensors.",
    "In general, the resolution of point clouds is directly depending on the quality of acquisition sensors.",
    "Resolution implies the level of detail and precision of representation of a 3D scene's geometry."
  ]
}